TASK_DESCRIPTION=When doey add-team masterplan runs, it creates panes 2-5 but Claude never starts on them. They remain bare bash shells. The add_team_from_def function in shell/doey-team-mgmt.sh has the worker launch code (lines ~985-1005) that calls doey_send_command for each worker pane, but it exits with code 2 and workers stay at bash prompt. The manager (pane 0) launches fine. Need to debug why worker launch fails for masterplan teams specifically.
